1.0.name: wordpress/chatlive
1.0.description:
Ingles:

Latest version of this fantastic plugin to support online through chat integrated into wordpress.

Some of its features are: * 1. Multisession users * 2. Choice of notification sounds * 3. Enabling and Disabling chat * 4. Easy integration for different languages * 5. Configuration is not required for the installation of the chat. It installs itself and displayed in any theme. * 6. Save all conversations, until the administrator decides to remove them. * 7. Nice design and is easily modified.

Español:

Ultima version de este fantastico plugin para dar soporte online mediante un chat integrado a wordpress.

Algunas de sus funcionalidades son: * 1. Multisesion de usuarios * 2. Eleccion de sonidos de notificaciones * 3. Habilitacion y deshabilitacion del chat * 4. Facil integracion para diferentes idiomas * 5. No es necesaria ninguna configuracion para la instalacion del chat. Se instala solo y se muestra en cualquier theme. * 6. Gua
